{{!-- 
Це код container файлу для person сторінки, 
в якому міститься код, котрий буде віддаватися по шляху (PATH) - "/person"
--}}

<div>
	{{#with person}}
	<main>
		{{> title data="Person" big=true}}
		<h3>{{name}}</h3>
		<section>
			<div>Age: {{age}}</div>
			<div>Gender: {{gender}}</div>
			<div> Address:
				{{#with address}}
				{{street}} , {{city}}, {{state}}, {{zip}}, {{country}}
				{{/with}}
			</div>
			<hr>
			<br>
			<div><b>Education</b>
				<ul>
					{{#each education}}
					<li>
						<div>Degree: {{degree}} </div>
						<div>Major: {{major}}</div>
						<div>University: {{university}}</div>
						<div>Graduated: {{graduationYear}}</div>
					</li>
					{{/each}}
				</ul>
				<br>
				<hr>
				<br>
				<div><b>Work experience</b>
					<ul>
						{{#each workExperience}}
						<li>
							<div><b>Company:</b> {{company}} </div>
							<div>Title: {{title}}</div>
							<div>Term: {{startDate}}–{{endDate}}</div>
							<br>
							<div>Responsibilities:
								{{!-- {{#each responsibilities}} --}}
								{{responsibilities}}</div>
							{{!-- {{/each}}</div> --}}
							<div>Year founded: {{year_founded}}</div>
							<div>Industry: {{industry}}</div>
							____________
							<div><b>Employees</Employees>
									{{#each employees}}
							</div>
							<div></div>
							<div></div>

							{{/each}}






						</li>
						{{/each}}
					</ul>




					</li>

					</ul>

		</section>
	</main>
	{{/with }}
</div>